      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "余裕あったらいけない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shouldn't I be relaxed?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.8961538553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、普通は緊張感というか……多少なりとも\nぴりぴりした空気になるんじゃないかと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I think it's usually more or less tense or ……\nmore or less tense.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.362820522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "別に。やることやってんだから\n今更、緊張なんてする訳ないっしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I'm doing what I'm supposed to do. I'm already doing\nwhat I'm supposed to do‚\nso there's no reason for me to be nervous now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9961538553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.062820522
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "kanaの頭の中にあるのは、成功するイメージだけ\n絶対にこのステージを成功させる。いや、させて当然",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The only thing in kana's mind is the image of success.\nI will definitely make this stage a success. No‚ i deserves it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.2961538553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "それにさ、ギャラもらってるんだから\n仕事はきっちりやんなきゃじゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ I'm getting paid‚\nso I have to do my job well‚ don't I?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.762820522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "つくづく思いますけど……\nkanaさんのメンタル、鋼みたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really think so. ……\nKana-san’s mentality is like steel!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.062820522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？　今更分かったの？\nkanaのアイドルとしての覚悟とプライド",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ha? You just figured it out now?\nkana's determination and pride as an idol",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.4961538553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "kanaは、スリクスは、二度と負けない\n観客動員数でも、ライブバトルでも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana and ⅢX will never lose again\nWhether it's in attendance or in live battles",
