    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ。どうだろ\nもう誰にも負けたくないってのは、間違いないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "hmm. What do you think?\nI definitely don't want to lose to anyone anymore.",
