      },
      "startTime": 92.0294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.6294871886
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "どうせやるんだったら、勝って一番になりたいじゃん\nkana達はそれが出来るくらい、超強いんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if I'm going to do it anyway‚\nI want to win and be the best‚ right?\nBecause Kanas' are so strong that we can do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.962820522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "それに、mihoもfranも全然好きじゃないけど\nステージの上のあいつらだけは、信用してるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I don't like miho and fran at all‚\nbut I trust them on stage.",
