      "text": "そこは強調しなくても……とにかく当面は\nみなさんなりのやり方を見守ることにします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "you don't need to emphasize that …… Anyway‚\nfor the time being‚ I'll be watching your way of doing things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今までのアイドルにはない何かを感じますから",
