        "en": "I feel something that has not been seen in idols up to now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.7961538553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.962820522
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？　{user}が担当してきた連中と\nスリクスを一緒にしないでくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Don't you compare ⅢX with the idol\n{user} has been in charge of?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.7294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.2653799295
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "実力も、プロとしての覚悟も、全然違うんだから！\n……さて、そろそろ仕事の時間。行ってくるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're completely different in terms of ability\nand professionalism!\n…… Well‚ it's time to get to work. I'm off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.4663006341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
