        "en": "Leave it to me. I'll make sure I get a good shot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.0294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "当然。さっきは全然役に立たなかったんだから\nせいぜい頑張んなよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. You were no help at all earlier.\nYou're doing best‚ aren't you?",
